payload.sql:
SELECT TOP (200000)
  t0.[Created] AS [Created],
  t0.[CountryCode] AS [CountryCode],
  COUNT(1) AS [TotalRecords],
  COUNT(1) AS [ProcessedFilesCount]
FROM [dbo].[MBPMemberCouponCount] AS t0

GROUP BY t0.[Created], t0.[CountryCode], DATEADD(day, DATEDIFF(day, 0, t0.[Created]), 0)
ORDER BY t0.[Created] DESC
